@startuml
title Long-Running Workflow Orchestration

participant Orchestrator
participant Gateway
participant Executor
participant Runtime
participant Approver

Orchestrator -> Gateway: start workflow execution
Gateway -> Runtime: create workflow state
Gateway -> Executor: start step 1
Executor --> Gateway: pending callback
Gateway --> Orchestrator: async accepted

... later ...

Approver -> Gateway: approval decision
Gateway -> Runtime: update state
Runtime --> Gateway: resume enabled
Gateway -> Executor: resume step
Executor --> Gateway: completion
Gateway -> Orchestrator: final result
@enduml
